abstract: Nasdaq Stock Market obtained clearance to sell a stake to Borse Dubai, paving the way for Nasdaq’s eventual acquisition of the OMX exchange in Stockholm.
snippet: Nasdaq Stock Market obtained clearance to sell a stake to Borse Dubai, paving the way for Nasdaq’s eventual acquisition of the OMX exchange in Stockholm.
lead_paragraph: Nasdaq Stock Market obtained clearance on Monday from the Committee on Foreign Investment in the United States to sell a stake to Borse Dubai, paving the way for Nasdaq’s eventual acquisition of the OMX exchange in Stockholm.

headline.main: U.S. Clears Sale of a Stake in Nasdaq
